reviewText: As my Dad PR1 Raymond F.Wohlford Jr. (deceased) was the only original team member and test jumper on the team when disbanded in 1964. I was thrilled to find this on DVD, I have a old VHS copy. Too bad the color is not restored, I do remember this from my youth. Recently showed it to friends who found it enteresting. Good Propoganda for Navy back in the 60's.
